Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.03,0:00:21.70,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,This reeks...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.28,0:00:25.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,of being fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:31.92,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz33.408\pos(391,114)\c&H000000&\3c&HF2D6DF&\frx4\fry328}Mold
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.71,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell. It's getting moldy again.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.71,0:00:34.92,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And I recently wiped off the mold too.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.92,0:00:37.96,Narration,Ryuuji (loud),0000,0000,0000,,It's something gentle and very sweet.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.46,0:00:38.55,Default,Ryuuji (mumbling),0000,0000,0000,,Where did I put that rag...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.92,0:00:44.35,Narration,Ryuuji (loud),0000,0000,0000,,And if you were able to put your eyes on it, then you would yearn for it.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.35,0:00:52.19,Narration,Aisaka Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the world has hidden it.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.19,0:00:54.98,Narration,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,To make sure that not just anyone can get their hands on it.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.86,0:00:58.65,Default,Ryuuji (mumbling),0000,0000,0000,,Shit, I can't wipe it off!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.95,0:01:03.07,Narration,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,But at some point, someone will find it.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.20,0:01:08.66,Narration,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That one person who is supposed to find it is also the one who will be able to find it.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.46,0:01:17.21,Narration,Taiga & Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:25.68,Ep Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(559,205)}Tiger & Dragon
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.51,0:01:25.93,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eco, eco, eco, ecology~
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.77,0:01:35.07,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Inko-chan, you're still resting? It's morning already.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.74,Default,Takasu Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,I got you!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.37,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,How cold of you, Ryuu-chan.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.37,0:01:49.92,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I told you last night that I have school from today on, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.92,0:01:54.59,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the opening ceremony.\NCongratulations on passing last year.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.59,0:01:57.76,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Should you really be sarcastic towards your son when he's going into his new school year?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.72,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the room is dark. Open the curtains!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.72,0:02:02.68,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,They're open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:10.94,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\bord1\frz331.259\3c&HC9F5EE&\c&H242C28&\move(531,212,531,520)\be1}The Takasu House
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.64,0:02:09.27,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,That's a huge apartment building.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.27,0:02:11.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of people live there.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.61,0:02:16.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,After it was built, the sun quit shining here and our laundry doesn't dry well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:13.90,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H262C28&\3c&HCFF4F1&\frz342.688\move(498,0,498,128)}HERE
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.99,0:02:19.36,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Every morning there's mold, moldiness, heaps of mold...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.36,0:02:23.58,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,That sharp look! You're beginning to look more and more like your dad!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.70,0:02:27.08,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3380)}...more and more like your dad!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare me to tha—!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.54,0:02:33.04,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so cool! Even more like your dad!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.46,0:02:40.72,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving already? What about my meal?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.09,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's where it always is.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.22,0:02:44.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.18,0:02:50.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That was the only thing I didn't want to hear.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.94,0:03:00.36,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of this look in my eyes, which you always praise, that I... I...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.57,Default,Random guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.95,Default,Random guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takasu!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.58,Default,Random guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.96,Alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wh—
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.58,0:03:09.58,Default,Random guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.29,Default,Random guys,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this and spare us!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.92,Default,Random guys,0000,0000,0000,,This is all we have! It's true!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.63,Default,Random guys,0000,0000,0000,,S-See? We're not annoying you, are we?!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.09,Alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.96,Default,Random guys,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.34,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I...
