Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.39,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H252E2F&\bord0\3c&HAFCBDB&\fnAubrey\fs18\frx332\fry2\pos(380,139)}Oohashi High School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.39,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H252E2F&\bord0\3c&HAFCBDB&\fnAubrey\fs20\frx332\fry2\frz1.288\pos(344,184)\fscx72.62837}General Affairs Department
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.68,0:03:32.60,Default,Man in window,0000,0000,0000,,Again? You sure pick up a lot of wallets.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.60,0:03:33.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.11,Default,Girls running by,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we end up in the same class again!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.11,0:03:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.28,Default,Girl #1,0000,0000,0000,,It's there!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.28,0:03:42.11,Default,Girl #2,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray, we're in the same class again!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.37,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, not this again...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.25,Default,Kitamura Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.83,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class again, aren't we, Takasu?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.55,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\c&H000000&\3c&HEBE1E3&\bord1.5\move(167,335,167,302)\fnAnnifont\i1\frx2\fry12\frz344.096\be1\fax0.4}Oohashi High School Opening Ceremony
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.96,0:04:00.88,Default,Speaker,0000,0000,0000,,And now this year's opening ceremony has ended.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.88,0:04:04.22,Default,Speaker,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please head towards your individual classrooms and prepare for homeroom.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.68,0:04:09.89,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A new class. It seems that I have to start off by clearing up all the misunderstandings again.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.10,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.98,0:04:15.52,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I already know, so it won't be necessary for everyone.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.73,0:04:23.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. There are people like him who understand.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And in this class...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.49,Default,Kushieda Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.33,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class this year too!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.95,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're in class C too, Kushieda?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.79,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, right? Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.79,0:04:40.84,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I appear from time to time around Kitamura.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.26,0:04:45.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kushieda Minori, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.01,0:04:49.93,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you remembered my full name! I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.27,0:04:58.86,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,And with that, let us passionately enjoy class in high spirits!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.86,0:04:59.44,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.86,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.44,Default,Punk,0000,0000,0000,,And then—
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.36,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Takasu?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.36,0:05:09.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just need to go the bathroom.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.87,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go on ahead.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.04,0:05:20.34,Default,Muttering in the background,0000,0000,0000,,Holy shit! He's already heading into a decisive battle!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.34,0:05:26.01,Default,More muttering,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu Ryuuji and Aisaka Taiga. The most dangerous ones are already clashing!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.76,0:05:35.52,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, she's so small, just like a doll. But somehow...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.44,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow there's this hateful...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.44,0:05:43.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,As if you'd get eaten if you missed one step...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.23,0:05:46.86,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's true! The delinquent Takasu and the Palmtop Tiger are—!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.86,0:05:47.28,Default,Other girl,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.78,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDBFDFC&\c&H4E5357&\fs20\frz25.011\fnBeatsville\pos(111,78)}Ferocity of a tiger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.78,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnBeatsville\fs20\3c&HFAFAFA&\c&H464646&\pos(595,198)\frz336.164}But small
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.78,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Palmtop... Tiger...?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.91,0:05:54.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! Palmtop Ti—
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.79,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.09,0:06:04.84,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's it for today.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.84,0:06:08.97,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Those who haven't turned in the new questionnaire, please come to the faculty office later, okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.05,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.35,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.77,0:06:19.52,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Taiga? You were late.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.52,0:06:24.02,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the doctor, and he said that it's caused by house dust.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.02,0:06:27.32,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,A modern-day illness, must be tough.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.94,0:06:33.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,So the Palmtop Tiger is friends with Kushieda Minori.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The one with problems here is me.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.41,0:06:37.45,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.21,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.42,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.54,0:06:44.59,Default,Girl in background,0000,0000,0000,,They were amazing, Aisaka-san and Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.67,Default,Guy in background,0000,0000,0000,,The Palmtop Tiger sure is strong.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.59,Default,Guy #2 in background,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, Takasu only {\i1}looks{\i0} scary. He's not actually a delinquent.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.51,Default,Girl #2 in background,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.47,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Seems it will be easier to clear up the misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.43,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, 'sup?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.48,0:07:04.77,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takasu-kun, you aren't lost about where to go with your life, are you...?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.06,0:07:05.65,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.65,0:07:08.94,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bu-Bu-But... I really need you to turn in your questionnaire.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.07,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,All of the other students have submitted theirs already.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry, I forg—
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.62,0:07:14.57,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so sorry! I'm so sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.57,0:07:16.37,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want some stranger coming in and telling you what to do
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.37,0:07:17.87,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,while you're still deciding on what to do with your life, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.16,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:21.46,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx0\fry16\frz357.255\pos(313,395)\bord0\shad1.5\bord0.5\3a&H96&\4c&H92A6C6&\c&HAED8E8&\be1}Fire Cabinet
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.79,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Time Zero will be ove—
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.27,0:07:47.15,Default,Ryuyuji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay...?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.65,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,My bag, my bag...
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just leave her be...
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.70,0:07:56.53,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.29,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What ar — What are you do — What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.16,Alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I just came here to get my—
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.41,0:08:06.50,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's your bag?! Isn't your seat the ne—
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.38,0:08:12.13,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I got the placements of the seats mix — mixed—!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she want my bag?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.68,0:08:24.52,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it already!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why, you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.82,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aisaka?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.58,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.25,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.21,0:08:51.80,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She's a mess.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.43,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,This room too.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.48,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad is in heaven, you see.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.98,0:09:19.20,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,He was so cool! He'd hide weekly magazines behind his shirt in case he got stabbed.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.83,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going numb just from the thought!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.12,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I look like you...
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.33,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having mountains of trouble, you know!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.00,0:09:31.92,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't have this face, no one would be afraid of me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.92,0:09:34.51,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,and I wouldn't end up getting involved with the Palmtop Tiger.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.34,0:09:37.30,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have more faith in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.51,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H4C4643&\bord1.5\3c&HE3E1DF&\fnComplete in Him\fs25\frz359.921\pos(328,356)}Best Driving Collection - Spring
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.76,0:09:39.51,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, the new questionnaire.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.23,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H675962&\fnBudHand\b1\fs25\frz354.325\pos(343,224)}To Kitamura Yuusaku
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.39,0:09:50.40,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,To Kitamura Yuusaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:50.36,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H675962&\fnBudHand\b1\fs25\frz348.323\frx10\fry16\pos(380,210)}To Kitamura Yuusaku
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:50.48,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H675962&\fnBudHand\b1\fs25\frx18\fry54\frz340.3\pos(457,203)}To Kitamura Yuusaku
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:50.61,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H675962&\fnBudHand\b1\fs20\frx2\fry294\frz14.551\pos(331,199)}From Aisaka Taiga
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:50.73,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H675962&\fnBudHand\b1\fs20\pos(361,189)\frx356\fry332\frz15.214}From Aisaka Taiga
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:50.86,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H675962&\fnBudHand\b1\fs20\frx354\fry344\frz10.97\pos(384,185)}From Aisaka Taiga
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.36,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H675962&\fnBudHand\b1\fs20\frz9.799\pos(409,184)}From Aisaka Taiga
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.52,0:09:54.40,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,From... Aisaka Taiga?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.36,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.87,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,"You put this in my bag by mistake, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.87,0:10:06.66,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine what's inside since I didn't peek!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll just return it to you, then!"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, I gotta reseal it!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.34,0:10:21.30,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She... She's one hell of a klutz, isn't she?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.02,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna sleep.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.65,0:10:44.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko... isn't supposed to be home yet, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.24,0:10:47.12,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, let's drink more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:49.00,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz9.974\3c&H5C31C4&\fnVAG Rounded Std Light\pos(476,202)}Takasu Yasuko\N{\fs16.000002\b1}Professional Name: Mirano
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.01,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVAG Rounded Std Light\pos(504,326)\frz351.3\c&H80332B&\3c&HF5F5F7&}At work
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Heeey...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The window's...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.52,0:11:17.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I know someone this small...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aisaka!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.29,0:11:37.75,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use a tissue!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.09,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What the...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.14,0:11:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...hell..
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.14,0:11:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.23,0:11:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.10,0:11:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...doing?!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.56,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.07,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about...?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.90,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that le—
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.82,0:12:01.53,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,—tter...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.11,0:12:07.45,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer live on now that you've found out about that. I have to die!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't try to kill me!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.24,0:12:12.08,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die, so I've got to kill you!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.66,0:12:15.83,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Or... you could forget all about it!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.21,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.92,0:12:25.38,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay, I'll just hit you on the head with this. Even if I can't kill you, I can send your memories flying away.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.55,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't send them flying!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.64,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, that letter—
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.64,0:12:29.26,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shut up, shut up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.31,0:12:34.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it, didn't you?! You read it, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.15,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to tell you, I didn't-
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.44,0:12:37.81,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't do.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.81,0:12:44.36,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So you have to forget all about that l-l-love letter!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.78,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was empty!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.37,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Em...pty...?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.87,0:12:57.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There was nothing inside.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.46,0:13:00.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky you didn't turn it over to Kitamura.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.92,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,So let's just leave this failure be and—
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.05,0:13:06.22,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.27,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Just how hungry are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I got tired of the convenience store.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.32,0:13:26.28,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Convenience store? What, don't your parents fe—
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.95,0:13:30.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has their family issues, I guess.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.20,0:13:30.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.66,0:13:40.67,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If you had just quietly handed over the bag earlier, things wouldn't have ended up like this.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.21,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,How do you intend to make up for it?!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's still stuck to your face.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.97,0:13:52.35,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that from a guy who was born only to add the scent of garlic to the oil used in this fried rice...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen here...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.28,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,How is a love letter embarrassing?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.28,0:14:09.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You see, that's not even close to being embarrassing. Just wait.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.25,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.66,0:14:22.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that is? You don't, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.00,0:14:27.88,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's a list of songs I would use if I were to put on a concert for the girl I like.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.51,0:14:31.22,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's a poem I wrote for her without realizing it.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,MDs to play while I'm on a car trip with her.{todo: note MDs=Minidiscs}
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.68,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a license, of course.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I have plans laid out for all seasons of the year.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.44,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Disgusting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.44,0:14:42.98,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Since I don't have the guts to confess to her, I just have to imagine like this.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.52,0:14:47.36,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's horribly miserable, but I don't think of it as embarrassing!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to have faith in yourself!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.65,0:14:53.37,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone beyond imagining and went and took action!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.70,0:14:57.12,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to think about the future, passionately, in high spirits!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.12,0:14:59.29,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"I present this to thee, Kushieda Minori."
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.29,0:15:02.12,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just like Kushieda Minori!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.46,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.04,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So you like Minori?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.13,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,How impudent.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.38,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Learn your place.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.43,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You're not one to talk!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.72,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?! You said you'd forget!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.43,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Goose, goosebumps!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.44,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Inko-chan. Did we wake you?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.98,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What are you showing me?! How disgusting!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying about my precious family?!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.24,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I-I—
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Are you going to present yourself to the visitor, Inko-chan?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.32,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and say your name!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.57,0:15:38.74,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,In{\alpha&HFF&}po!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.74,0:15:39.29,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,Inpo!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.71,0:15:48.21,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, you see, Inko-chan isn't feeling well today...
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.13,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's already this late!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.59,0:15:57.55,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,E-Either way, we're birds of the same feather! I won't tell anyone about the letter! Can't you be okay with that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.55,0:15:58.22,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.22,0:16:01.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! No wait, you've already gotten a meal, just leave!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.73,0:16:05.69,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, please leave? My wacky mom is about to come home!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.31,0:16:06.98,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No {\alpha&HFF&}fucking way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.98,0:16:07.52,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No fucking{\alpha&HFF&} way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.52,0:16:08.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No fucking way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust you.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.49,0:16:13.24,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And besides...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.82,0:16:19.24,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,How are love letters? They're not fashionable anymore, are they?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.91,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you fidgeting now?!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.91,0:16:27.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you advice on romantic relationships any time, but it's already late, so how about tomorrow...?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.42,0:16:31.09,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You'll help me?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.09,0:16:33.55,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I will. I will I will I will! I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.05,0:16:40.56,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Anything, right? You'll obey me like a dog? You'll do anything to the extreme?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.93,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will. I swear!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.27,0:16:46.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's just end it at that, okay? Okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.82,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,How did she get in through the window?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.16,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.82,0:16:57.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.61,0:17:00.53,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay. It's close, and I've got this wooden sword.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.79,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's just dangerous.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.04,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that hole...
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.79,0:17:10.25,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that? I can just cover it up with some paper.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.34,0:17:11.92,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.21,0:17:14.80,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You can use this.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.59,0:17:18.39,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If it ends up costing money, I'll pay you later.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.01,0:17:21.22,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.72,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.15,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did she just call me by my first name?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is the Takasu residenc—
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.16,0:17:48.58,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get the hell over here! You're—{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.21,0:17:56.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.63,0:17:57.51,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You hung up, didn't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.76,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Come over where?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.76,0:18:03.47,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The veranda, why?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.27,0:18:12.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.48,0:18:15.36,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd do anything, just like a dog, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.69,0:18:19.53,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that was about yesterday's thing about Kitamura—
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.53,0:18:23.95,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't come, you know what will happen, don't you? I can show you what will happen if you want me to...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.12,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you see...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.75,0:18:31.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait ten more minutes! The seasoned rice will be done in ten more minutes!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.17,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Three?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.30,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You want some too?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.15,0:19:02.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.66,0:19:10.29,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.00,0:19:11.71,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.33,0:19:14.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's open?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.00,0:19:19.13,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this smell?!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.34,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.14,0:19:26.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Something smells horrible.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.19,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aisaka!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka. Aisaka! {\i1}Aisaka!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.19,0:19:42.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Your kitchen!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.32,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to—!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.86,0:19:46.91,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Please, allow me to clean your kitchen!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.91,0:19:55.58,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What, sleeping again?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.13,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She looks handcrafted...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.76,0:20:06.09,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The sleeping Aisaka really looked like a doll.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.85,0:20:11.56,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The house had no trace of anyone really living there. It looked like it was part of someone's doll house.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.64,0:20:16.77,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,But it was too large to be someone's doll house.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.73,0:20:23.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take fifteen minutes, I guess.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.05,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's... this...?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.81,0:20:51.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.68,0:20:55.56,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still at it, but it's a lot cleaner now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.69,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It was horrid!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.65,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The water clogged up in the sink was rotten.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.65,0:21:03.19,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The drainage was awfully moldy and all the waste was like hell spawn.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And the room was full of dust...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.28,0:21:11.79,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Trespassing. Forced cleaning. You didn't go around marking the place, did you, dog?!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.79,0:21:12.95,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dog?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.95,0:21:17.54,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to apologize to the other dogs. You're a mongrel of a dog.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.79,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Mon-grel.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.79,0:21:22.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What an ungrateful bitch, when other people have—!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.43,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's your table prayer?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.27,0:21:39.90,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Dear god of rice and producers of this product, I thank you for this meal!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.11,0:21:42.32,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh you...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.57,0:21:46.65,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your nose stopped dripping.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.15,0:21:50.07,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, since the room's all clean...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.08,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shut up!{\i0}
