Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.54,0:21:56.91,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0010,,Disoriented agreement.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.91,0:21:57.66,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0010,,Surfacing misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.66,0:21:59.08,Default,Ryuiji,0000,0000,0010,,The power of genes.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.08,0:22:00.75,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0010,,Taiga, you...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.75,0:22:02.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0010,,You're one hell of a klutz.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.63,0:22:04.34,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0010,,Shut up and rot.
